<section class="contact" id="contacto">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-card">
      <span class="eyebrow">Contacto</span>
      <h2>Hablemos de tu proyecto</h2>
      <p>
        Cuéntame qué necesitas y conversemos sobre cómo la IA y una ingeniería sólida pueden
        acelerar tu próximo proyecto.
      </p>
      <div class="contact-icons">
        <a
          class="icon-btn icon-email"
          href="mailto:pablo.cornejo.v@gmail.com"
          aria-label="Escríbeme un correo a pablo.cornejo.v@gmail.com"
        >
          <span class="icon-circle">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"></rect><path
                d="m22 6-10 7L2 6"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </span>
          <span class="icon-label">Email</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="icon-btn icon-whatsapp"
          href="https://wa.me/56957591164"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          aria-label="Escríbeme por WhatsApp al +56 9 5759 1164"
        >
          <span class="icon-circle">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32"
              ><path
                d="M16 3C9.4 3 4 8.4 4 15c0 2.4.7 4.6 1.9 6.5L4 29l7.7-2c1.9 1 4 1.6 6.3 1.6 6.6 0 12-5.4 12-12S22.6 3 16 3Zm0 21.8c-1.9 0-3.7-.5-5.3-1.4l-.4-.2-4.6 1.2 1.2-4.4-.2-.4C5.8 18 5.2 16.5 5.2 15c0-5.9 4.9-10.8 10.8-10.8S26.8 9.1 26.8 15 21.9 24.8 16 24.8Zm5.9-8.1c-.3-.2-1.9-.9-2.2-1-.3-.1-.5-.2-.7.2-.2.3-.8 1-.9 1.2-.2.2-.3.2-.6.1-.3-.2-1.3-.5-2.5-1.5-.9-.8-1.5-1.8-1.7-2.1-.2-.3 0-.5.1-.6.1-.1.3-.3.4-.5.1-.2.2-.3.3-.5.1-.2 0-.4 0-.5 0-.2-.7-1.7-1-2.3-.3-.6-.5-.5-.7-.5h-.6c-.2 0-.5.1-.8.4-.3.3-1 1-1 2.4s1.1 2.8 1.2 3c.1.2 2.2 3.3 5.3 4.6.7.3 1.3.5 1.8.6.7.2 1.4.2 1.9.1.6-.1 1.9-.8 2.2-1.5.3-.7.3-1.4.2-1.5-.1-.1-.3-.2-.6-.3Z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </span>
          <span class="icon-label">WhatsApp</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="icon-btn icon-linkedin"
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/pablo-cornejo-villarroel-43973a59/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          aria-label="Mi perfil de LinkedIn"
        >
          <span class="icon-circle">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"
              ><path
                d="M4.98 3.5C4.98 4.9 3.9 6 2.5 6S0 4.9 0 3.5 1.1 1 2.5 1s2.48 1.1 2.48 2.5zM.5 8.4h4V23h-4V8.4zM8.7 8.4h3.83v2h.05c.53-1 1.84-2.05 3.79-2.05 4.06 0 4.81 2.67 4.81 6.14V23h-4v-6.75c0-1.61-.03-3.68-2.24-3.68-2.25 0-2.6 1.75-2.6 3.56V23h-4V8.4z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </span>
          <span class="icon-label">LinkedIn</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <a href="mailto:pablo.cornejo.v@gmail.com" class="btn btn-primary">Cotizar proyecto</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .contact-card {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 780px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    padding: var(--space-7);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .contact-card::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px;
    left: -1px;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--cyan);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--cyan);
  }

  .contact-card::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -1px;
    right: -1px;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--magenta);
    border-right: 2px solid var(--magenta);
  }

  .contact-card p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .contact-icons {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
  }

  .icon-btn {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .icon-btn .icon-circle {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--bg-elevated-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    transition:
      transform 0.15s ease,
      border-color 0.15s ease,
      box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .icon-btn svg {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
  }

  .icon-whatsapp svg,
  .icon-linkedin svg {
    fill: currentColor;
  }

  .icon-email svg {
    fill: none;
    stroke: currentColor;
  }

  .icon-btn .icon-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .icon-btn:hover .icon-circle,
  .icon-btn:focus-visible .icon-circle {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .icon-btn:hover .icon-label,
  .icon-btn:focus-visible .icon-label {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .icon-email .icon-circle {
    color: var(--cyan);
  }
  .icon-email:hover .icon-circle,
  .icon-email:focus-visible .icon-circle {
    border-color: var(--cyan);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px 2px rgba(var(--cyan-rgb), 0.4);
  }

  .icon-whatsapp .icon-circle {
    color: var(--green);
  }
  .icon-whatsapp:hover .icon-circle,
  .icon-whatsapp:focus-visible .icon-circle {
    border-color: var(--green);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px 2px rgba(var(--green-rgb), 0.4);
  }

  .icon-linkedin .icon-circle {
    color: var(--magenta);
  }
  .icon-linkedin:hover .icon-circle,
  .icon-linkedin:focus-visible .icon-circle {
    border-color: var(--magenta);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px 2px rgba(var(--magenta-rgb), 0.4);
  }
</style>
